    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到一款充满乐趣和惊喜的猫咪竞速与养成游戏！在这里，你将体验到一个充满创意与欢乐的猫咪世界。在这个令人兴奋的冒险中，你可以：<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/b70b87f0a4cbd9a49b22c008550b572f.poster.avif?t=1735470555\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/b70b87f0a4cbd9a49b22c008550b572f.webm?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/b70b87f0a4cbd9a49b22c008550b572f.mp4?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索10种以上独特的竞速模式：</strong>准备好迎接挑战吧！“贪食蛇猫猫”、“查酒驾大作战”、“德古拉喵”、“过山车地铁”，以及其他新颖的赛道模式，体验不同的游戏玩法和竞争乐趣。每个模式都有独特的规则和策略，让你在每场比赛中都能感受到新鲜感。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/02d45603d87b11fc20ebcbb2711eb582.poster.avif?t=1735470555\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/02d45603d87b11fc20ebcbb2711eb582.webm?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/02d45603d87b11fc20ebcbb2711eb582.mp4?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/f53bba2618ccc95f23a2f862b253a0e9.poster.avif?t=1735470555\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/f53bba2618ccc95f23a2f862b253a0e9.webm?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/f53bba2618ccc95f23a2f862b253a0e9.mp4?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>繁殖系统与超能力：</strong>通过独特的繁殖系统，解锁你猫咪的搞怪超能力！想象一下，拥有“尾巴直升机”的猫咪可以轻松飞跃障碍，或是其他奇特的技能，让你的猫咪在比赛中脱颖而出。组合不同的能力，创造出独一无二的猫咪，展现你的创意！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/695e697fb2dd23270f9a1de7423c736f.poster.avif?t=1735470555\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/695e697fb2dd23270f9a1de7423c736f.webm?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/695e697fb2dd23270f9a1de7423c736f.mp4?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/50be24384df4775ba1073a9c471685e6.poster.avif?t=1735470555\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/50be24384df4775ba1073a9c471685e6.webm?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/50be24384df4775ba1073a9c471685e6.mp4?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与朋友的猫咪对战：</strong>邀请朋友们一起加入比赛，看看谁的猫咪更胜一筹！在竞争的同时，你还可以使用各种幽默的道具，恶搞对手的猫咪，增添更多欢笑与乐趣。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/6313e33786e37a2b6b425c715126badc.poster.avif?t=1735470555\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/6313e33786e37a2b6b425c715126badc.webm?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/6313e33786e37a2b6b425c715126badc.mp4?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>数字化你的现实猫咪：</strong>将你心爱的现实猫咪转化为游戏中的数字分身，带上它们的独特外观和个性。你可以为它们定制服装和配饰，让它们在游戏中大放异彩，尽情展现个性。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/71fb3d2fe51eaab97a08aaa10486d035.poster.avif?t=1735470555\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/71fb3d2fe51eaab97a08aaa10486d035.webm?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257590/extras/71fb3d2fe51eaab97a08aaa10486d035.mp4?t=1735470555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是竞速游戏的爱好者，还是猫咪的狂热粉丝，这款游戏都将带给你无尽的欢乐与挑战！快来加入我们，开启一段属于你的猫咪冒险吧！</p>",
